
> ðŸŽ¥ To make `demo.gif`:
> 1. Record with [`asciinema`](https://asciinema.org/):  
>    `asciinema rec -c "vigil cpu; vigil mem; vigil exec -- sleep 1" demo.cast`  
> 2. Convert to GIF: `agg demo.cast demo.gif` (install `agg` via pip)

